{"tid":1458943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇六七暴動放炸彈，死50人，2000人被捕，都係失敗收場？","createTime":"2019-08-12T15:31:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T16:40:11.000Z","uid":73915,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"964045d7ea91958f9268ad6bd070ac231d1d041c","tid":1458943,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:31:53.000Z","msg":"好似有排未到果種程度，大家要諗下點贏<br />\n<br />\n六七暴動<br />\n<br />\n目標<br />\n為死難工人復仇，最終推翻港英政府<br />\n<br />\n方法<br />\n聚集、罷工、罷市、遊行、放火、放炸彈、抗議、殺警、槍戰<br />\n<br />\n結果<br />\n推翻港英政府失敗<br />\n港英政府推行經濟改革，並且開始反貪<br />\n強化香港人恐共及反共情緒<br />\n左派勢力減弱，直至香港回歸前<br />\n香港移民潮<br />\n小巴合法化"},{"pid":"a83d22b1dc26b37b85968fcbf72cb0a34ebea881","tid":1458943,"uid":145423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:34:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e889e0bbb8151257081cf611a937bb7727962d45","tid":1458943,"uid":41355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:34:56.000Z","msg":"開頭個陣市民係同情左派<br />\n但去到後面無差別炸人失晒民心<br />\n<br />\n=========================================<br />\n覺唔覺得太多post太亂？我整左個策略、行動、文宣方向精華集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1444217/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1444217/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFUfDD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFUfDD.png&h=51ddb9e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">機場檢討POST懶人包</span></strong><br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1458355/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1458355/page/1</a><br />\n我係空管主任，我想講今日機場真係呢兩個幾月黎香港人贏得最靚既一仗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1458321/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1458321/page/1</a><br />\n有消息嘗試用舉牌方式同人講<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457623/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457623/page/1</a><br />\n我覺得今日散水無錯，互屌先係真中計<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457903/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457903/page/1</a><br />\n[賽後檢討] 今日機場有無散水既都麻煩入一入黎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457735/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457735/page/1</a><br />\n下次搞再機場唔該幫下啲旅客<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457517/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457517/page/1</a><br />\n今日機場事件有少少諗法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457187/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457187/page/1</a><br />\n我係散水撚，我係嚟道歉嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n需要人手報料/update/宣傳呀"},{"pid":"538742fe8332f83a5ae669e91cd2adc444aadcfa","tid":1458943,"uid":81518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:35:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"278eba9a612d497e928810fbd9cfed584ee9c9c9","tid":1458943,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:36:27.000Z","msg":"[賽後檢討] 抗爭者進化史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1458526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1458526</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a5ae1f08c77e78fdd13ad64913d6858204f45f13","tid":1458943,"uid":92340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:38:05.000Z","msg":"有抗爭史統計過武力抗爭既失敗率有8成<br />\n反而和理非成功率有8成"},{"pid":"57f8d4af39b2c2bccce552d8565da2f0a80b62ee","tid":1458943,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"964045d7ea91958f9268ad6bd070ac231d1d041c","tid":1458943,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:31:53.000Z","msg":"好似有排未到果種程度，大家要諗下點贏<br />\n<br />\n六七暴動<br />\n<br />\n目標<br />\n為死難工人復仇，最終推翻港英政府<br />\n<br />\n方法<br />\n聚集、罷工、罷市、遊行、放